thread.title: AAS

author: AAS
title: AAS
text:
All the staff at Servcorp are wonderful. We have had Sarah and Phoebe assist us with casual work and their standard is far above any temp agency we have ever used before. They are both one of a kind, hard to find and hard working. They are also extremely professional. Phoebe is also a great cook!
Can't recommend them enough. Thank you for all your help - you've both made my job so much easier.
